listitem.para:
the tutorials are divided in two drop-down tabs:

tutorialsA: these use data structures/types that are known to pressio. 
Pressio recognizes them and has built-in support for kernels to operate on them;

tutorialsB: these use data structures/types that are unknown to pressio. 
Pressio detects them as arbitrary types, and the user has to provide kernels for operating on them;
